{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"This talk is about righting writing wrongs."},{"time":4000,"text":"No, the sound's not faulty -- righting writing wrongs."},{"time":7000,"text":"The Middle East is huge,"},{"time":10000,"text":"and with all our problems, one thing's for sure: we love to laugh."},{"time":13000,"text":"I think humor is a great way to celebrate our differences."},{"time":16000,"text":"We need to take our responsibilities seriously,"},{"time":18000,"text":"but not ourselves."},{"time":20000,"text":"Don't get me wrong: it's not like we don't have comedy in the Middle East."},{"time":23000,"text":"I grew up at a time when iconic actors"},{"time":25000,"text":"from Kuwait, Syria, Egypt"},{"time":27000,"text":"used laughter to unite the region,"},{"time":30000,"text":"just as football can."},{"time":32000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":35000,"text":"Now is the time for us to laugh at ourselves,"},{"time":37000,"text":"before others can laugh with us."},{"time":40000,"text":"This is the story of the rise and rise of stand-up comedy in the Middle East --"},{"time":43000,"text":"a stand-up uprising, if you will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"Working in London as TV maker and writer,"},{"time":50000,"text":"I quickly realized"},{"time":52000,"text":"that comedy connects audiences."},{"time":55000,"text":"Now, the best breeding ground for good comic writing"},{"time":58000,"text":"is the stand-up comedy circuit,"},{"time":60000,"text":"where they just happen to say that you kill when you do well"},{"time":62000,"text":"and you bomb when you do badly."},{"time":64000,"text":"An unfortunate connection for us maybe,"},{"time":66000,"text":"but it reminds me"},{"time":68000,"text":"that we'd like to thank one man for, over the past decade,"},{"time":71000,"text":"working tirelessly"},{"time":72000,"text":"to support comedians all around the world,"},{"time":75000,"text":"specifically comedians"},{"time":77000,"text":"with a Middle Eastern background."},{"time":79000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":82000,"text":"Like my good friends, Dean and Maysoon, at the bottom of the screen,"},{"time":85000,"text":"who, two years after 9/11,"},{"time":87000,"text":"started a festival to change the way"},{"time":89000,"text":"Middle Easterners are perceived in the world."},{"time":92000,"text":"It's still going strong, with positive press to die for."},{"time":96000,"text":"Also, three guys working for years in Los Angeles,"},{"time":99000,"text":"an Iranian, a Palestinian and an Egyptian,"},{"time":102000,"text":"created the aptly named Axis of Evil comedy act."},{"time":106000,"text":"And wherever they went,"},{"time":108000,"text":"they killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"Now, I didn't start this fire, but I did pour petrol on it."},{"time":113000,"text":"I moved to Dubai as the head of original content"},{"time":116000,"text":"for a Western TV network."},{"time":118000,"text":"My job was to connect the brand with a Middle Eastern audience."},{"time":123000,"text":"Now, the American head of programming"},{"time":126000,"text":"wanted new local Arabic comedy."},{"time":129000,"text":"In a thick Arabic accent, my brain went,"},{"time":132000,"text":"\"Berfect.\""},{"time":134000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":136000,"text":"Now, I had friends in the U.S."},{"time":138000,"text":"who had started a successful new tribe."},{"time":142000,"text":"And I had every intention of taking this tribe"},{"time":144000,"text":"from being outliers in the Middle East"},{"time":146000,"text":"and pushing them over the tipping point"},{"time":148000,"text":"towards success."},{"time":150000,"text":"Now, as with any new idea, it wasn't easy."},{"time":152000,"text":"I had four phases to this plan."},{"time":154000,"text":"First, we'd need to buy content from the West and air it."},{"time":157000,"text":"Then I'd bring my friends, and we'd show local amateurs how it's done."},{"time":160000,"text":"We would film that and air it,"},{"time":162000,"text":"and then I could work with the local amateurs and write new comedy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"I excitedly presented this to the big boss,"},{"time":167000,"text":"and his reaction was, \"Um, I don't get it.\""},{"time":172000,"text":"So I retreated back to my cave"},{"time":174000,"text":"and continued to support and produce comedy"},{"time":176000,"text":"and let my friends use my couch"},{"time":178000,"text":"as a regional operations hub."},{"time":181000,"text":"Now, fast forward two years, to early 2007."},{"time":184000,"text":"The earth rotated, as did our management,"},{"time":187000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":189000,"text":"and as if by divine intervention,"},{"time":191000,"text":"things came together"},{"time":193000,"text":"to help this revolution take shape."},{"time":196000,"text":"Here's how the dots connected."},{"time":198000,"text":"First, the Axis guys recorded a Comedy Central special"},{"time":201000,"text":"that aired in the States,"},{"time":203000,"text":"and it was getting great hits on YouTube."},{"time":205000,"text":"Our new French CEO"},{"time":207000,"text":"believed in the power of positive PR ..."},{"time":209000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":211000,"text":"and ideas du bon marche."},{"time":214000,"text":"Let's just say \"value for money.\""},{"time":216000,"text":"I produced in Dubai a show for Ahmed Ahmed"},{"time":219000,"text":"to showcase his new Axis special to a packed room."},{"time":221000,"text":"I invited our new CEO,"},{"time":223000,"text":"and as soon as he realized we had a room packed full of laughing infidels,"},{"time":226000,"text":"his reaction was very simple:"},{"time":228000,"text":"\"Let's make this happen."},{"time":231000,"text":"And one more thing: No, don't F it up.\""},{"time":234000,"text":"So I quickly went to work"},{"time":236000,"text":"with a great team around me."},{"time":238000,"text":"I happened to find"},{"time":240000,"text":"a funny guy to present it in Arabic,"},{"time":242000,"text":"who is originally Korean,"},{"time":245000,"text":"a perfect fit for the Axis of Evil."},{"time":247000,"text":"This is all true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"Now, while preparing for the tour,"},{"time":251000,"text":"I had to remind the guys to be culturally sensitive."},{"time":253000,"text":"I used the three Bs of stand-up don'ts"},{"time":255000,"text":"as I call them in the Middle East:"},{"time":258000,"text":"blue content, keep it clean; beliefs, not religion;"},{"time":261000,"text":"and the third B, bolitics."},{"time":264000,"text":"Stay away from bolitics in the Middle East."},{"time":267000,"text":"Oh course, you might think, what's left"},{"time":269000,"text":"without bolitics, sex and religion, how can you make people laugh?"},{"time":271000,"text":"I'd say, watch any successful well-written,"},{"time":274000,"text":"family-friendly sitcom in the West"},{"time":276000,"text":"for your answers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"Now, were the Axis successful?"},{"time":282000,"text":"In five countries, in just under a month,"},{"time":284000,"text":"we had thousands of fanatical fans come and see them live."},{"time":287000,"text":"We had millions see them on TV and on TV news."},{"time":290000,"text":"In Jordan, we had His Majesty the King come and see them."},{"time":293000,"text":"In fact, they were so successful"},{"time":295000,"text":"that you could buy a pirated copy of their DVD,"},{"time":297000,"text":"even before it was released in the Middle East."},{"time":299000,"text":"Anywhere you go."},{"time":301000,"text":"So everywhere we went,"},{"time":303000,"text":"we auditioned amateurs."},{"time":305000,"text":"We filmed that process and aired a documentary."},{"time":308000,"text":"I called it \"Three Guys and Wonho.\""},{"time":311000,"text":"It really is his name."},{"time":315000,"text":"And all this TV and Internet exposure"},{"time":318000,"text":"has led to a great many"},{"time":320000,"text":"recruits to our cause."},{"time":322000,"text":"In Dubai this year, we've just had"},{"time":324000,"text":"the first all-women's, homegrown stand-up show."},{"time":326000,"text":"And notice two of them are wearing headscarves,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and yes, even they can laugh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"Dubai, to me, is like a hand"},{"time":333000,"text":"that supports anyone who wants to make things happen."},{"time":336000,"text":"20 years ago,"},{"time":338000,"text":"no one had heard of it."},{"time":340000,"text":"Look at it now."},{"time":342000,"text":"With an inspirational leader, I think this year,"},{"time":344000,"text":"the opening of the tallest tower in the world"},{"time":346000,"text":"is like adding a finger to that hand,"},{"time":348000,"text":"that points at all those"},{"time":350000,"text":"who spread fallacious stories about us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"Now, in three short years, we've come a long way"},{"time":361000,"text":"with stand-up comedy shows happening even in Saudi Arabia."},{"time":364000,"text":"These comics are now going to the New York festival."},{"time":367000,"text":"And the Lebanese, brilliant Lebanese,"},{"time":369000,"text":"Nemr Abou Nassar, we featured in our first tour,"},{"time":371000,"text":"has just been performing in L.A.'s legendary comedy clubs."},{"time":374000,"text":"So clearly, from the inside, we are doing our best to change our image,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and it's exploding."},{"time":379000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":381000,"text":"So, as for the outsiders looking in,"},{"time":384000,"text":"watch the CNN report on the second Amman Comedy Festival."},{"time":387000,"text":"The reporter did a great job, and I thank her,"},{"time":390000,"text":"but somebody forgot to send the positive PR email"},{"time":393000,"text":"to the person operating the automatic news ticker that appears at the bottom."},{"time":396000,"text":"For example, when Dean talks,"},{"time":399000,"text":"the ticker says, \"U.S.: Suspect gave 'actionable intel.\""},{"time":402000,"text":"Well, if you're used to listening to comedians,"},{"time":405000,"text":"then I'm not surprised."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407000,"text":"Sadly, this leads me to another three Bs"},{"time":409000,"text":"that represents how the media in the West"},{"time":412000,"text":"talks about us as bombers, billionaires"},{"time":414000,"text":"and belly dancers."},{"time":417000,"text":"Enough."},{"time":419000,"text":"We're not all angry fanatics"},{"time":421000,"text":"who want to kill the infidel."},{"time":423000,"text":"We have a positive story to tell"},{"time":425000,"text":"and image to sell."},{"time":427000,"text":"In fact, one thing's for sure, in my experience,"},{"time":430000,"text":"we love to laugh like hell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436000,"text":"Here are three questions that I like to use"},{"time":438000,"text":"to test the truthiness of our representation"},{"time":441000,"text":"in any media story."},{"time":443000,"text":"One: Is the Middle East"},{"time":445000,"text":"being shown in a current time"},{"time":447000,"text":"and correct context?"},{"time":450000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":455000,"text":"Two: Do the Middle Eastern characters"},{"time":458000,"text":"laugh or smile"},{"time":461000,"text":"without showing the whites of their eyes?"},{"time":463000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":465000,"text":"Three: Is the Middle Eastern character"},{"time":468000,"text":"being played by one?"},{"time":473000,"text":"Clearly, there are wrongs that need to be righted."},{"time":476000,"text":"We've started in our region."},{"time":478000,"text":"My challenge to the rest of the world"},{"time":480000,"text":"is please, start using"},{"time":482000,"text":"positive Middle Eastern images in your stories."},{"time":484000,"text":"For inspiration, go to one of our festivals,"},{"time":486000,"text":"go online, drop us a line."},{"time":488000,"text":"Let's change the narrative together"},{"time":491000,"text":"and let's start righting writing wrongs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494000,"text":"I'd like to end, before going back to the Middle East,"},{"time":496000,"text":"with a quote from one of the greatest Sheikhs"},{"time":498000,"text":"to put quill to parchment."},{"time":500000,"text":"As my father likes to call him, \"Asheikh Azubare;\""},{"time":503000,"text":"as my mother would say, \"Shakespeare.\""},{"time":505000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":507000,"text":"\"And now we go in content"},{"time":509000,"text":"to liberty and not to banishment.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":511000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}